MIME Crosses Above Average Analyst Target
In recent trading, shares of Mimecast Ltd have crossed above the average analyst 12-month target price of $28.88, changing hands for $28.97/share. When a stock reaches the target an analyst has set, the analyst logically has two ways to react: downgrade on valuation, or, re-adjust their target price to a higher level.

