IPO Preview: Mimecast Ltd. - Mimecast (NASDAQ:MIME) | Seeking AlphaSign in / Join NowGO»IPO Preview: Mimecast Ltd.Nov.19.15 | About: Mimecast (MIME) IPOdesktop Value, IPOs, long onlyIPOpremiumSummaryGrowth rate decline: 32% for 2014; 31% for 2015; 22% for first six months.70% gross profit for Sept. six months.Net income -1% of revenue for Sept. six months, almost breakeven. 15,200 customers.Based in London, United Kingdom, Mimecast Ltd. (NASDAQ:MIME) scheduled an $85 million IPO on Nasdaq with a market capitalization of $594 million at a price range midpoint of $11 for Thursday, Nov. 19, 2015.
The full IPO calendar is available at IPOpremium.
